com.yantra.yfc.rcp

Interface IYRCPaginatedSearchAndListComposite

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IYRCComposite, IYRCSearchAndListComposite

    public interface IYRCPaginatedSearchAndListComposite
extends IYRCSearchAndListComposite
    The search and list composite which need to show paginated result should implement this interface.The following pagination strategies are supported.
    • GENERIC
    • ROWNUM
    • RESULTSET
    • NEXTPAGE

    If no pagination strategey is provided it defaults to GENERIC. Not all features are available in all pagination strategies. Trying to use a feature that is not supported in a given strategy will result in a YRCPaginationException. Screens which make pagination calls should set YRCApiContext.setPaginationRequired(boolean) as true else normal api calls will take place.

    See Also:
    YRCPaginationNavigator, YRCPaginationData, YRCPaginationException
